      "category": "context",
      "fact": "Luis Suárez bit Italy's Giorgio Chiellini on the shoulder in Uruguay's 1-0 win on 24 June 2014 — his third biting incident in football. FIFA banned him for 9 international matches and 4 months from all football. Uruguay still advanced.",
